import MasterPage from "./pages/MasterPage"
import DevelopmentPage from "./pages/DevelopmentPage"
import ReleasePage from "./pages/ReleasePage"

import shketDevImg from "./assets/shket-dev.png"
import narutoMod from "./assets/naruto-mod.jpg"
import engRef from "./assets/english-grammar-reference.png"
import dataScience from "./assets/data-science.png"

export const MASTER_PATH = "/master"
export const DEVELOPMENT_PATH = "/development"
export const RELEASE_PATH = "/release"

export const routes = [
  {path: MASTER_PATH, Component: MasterPage, title: "master"},
  {path: DEVELOPMENT_PATH, Component: DevelopmentPage, title: "development"},
  {path: RELEASE_PATH, Component: ReleasePage, title: "release"},
]

export const releases = [
  {name: "shket-dev", image: shketDevImg, description: "My epic website"},
  {name: "NarutoMod", image: narutoMod, description: "Minecraft. Naruto. Legendary compilation. 1.15.2"},
  {name: "English Grammar Reference", image: engRef, description: "latex? No, LaTeX! Speak proper, seem smart."},
  {name: "Data science", image: dataScience, description: "And some beautiful plots"},
]
